  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nRight now its only possible to get the version-info via `/debug/metrics/version`\r\n\r\nBeing able to get the version of a running node via a standardized way (prometheus) will make it easier to run and maintain the process.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nI suggest using a gauge, just like it is used for golang-info\r\n\r\n```\r\ngo_info{version=\"go1.20.5\"} 1\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt could be shown as\r\n\r\n```\r\nerigon_info{version=\"2.45.1-stable\",commit=\"29f8e97cf7adc0210191a7081ec288cd8aca34b1\"} 1\r\n```\r\n",
